item.title: CVE-2018-16856|2024-08-05T10:32:54.143Z -- %5Bunknown%5D -- openstack-octavia
item.description: In a default Red Hat Openstack Platform Director installation, openstack-octavia before versions openstack-octavia 2.0.2-5 and openstack-octavia-3.0.1-0.20181009115732 creates log files that are readable by all users. Sensitive information such as private keys can appear in these log files allowing for information exposure.
